Edison May Sign Kolubara Contract on June 21, Politika Reports

-- B y   M i s h a   S a v i c
-- 
2011-06-09T06:46:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/edison-may-sign-kolubara-contract-on-june-21-politika-reports.html
Edison SpA (EDN)  of  Italy  may on June 21
sign a preliminary contract with  Elektroprivreda Srbije ,
 Serbia ’s state-run power company, for completing the coal-fired
Kolubara B plant,  Politika  newspaper reported.  Edison, the sole bidder for Kolubara B, offered to finish
the plant in five years with an installed capacity of 750
megawatts instead of 700 megawatts, the newspaper said, citing
Petar Skundric, an adviser to Serbia’s premier.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Misha Savic in Belgrade at 
 msavic2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  